      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable, well-maintained ride? This vehicle is in good condition and has been well cared for over the years! You'll find a clean, functional interior with normal signs of everyday use \u2014 nothing that gets in the way of comfort or enjoyment. The exterior presents nicely with only minor cosmetic blemishes typical of a used vehicle at this age. Mechanically, it runs well and is ready to take on your daily commute or weekend adventures. A genuinely solid car at a fair price \u2014 come take it for a spin!",
