    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we're proud to provide an honest, thorough account of what you'll be getting. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use; no significant dents or rust to report. The interior is clean and well-maintained, with upholstery showing moderate wear but no tears, stains, or damage. All major features and controls function as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, with no known mechanical issues; routine maintenance has been kept up to date. The tires have solid tread remaining, and brakes are in good working order. This is a dependable vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
