      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a vehicle that truly stands out from the crowd? This car is in exceptional, mint condition \u2014 it looks and feels nearly new, inside and out! The interior is spotless with no noticeable wear, the exterior shines with no significant blemishes, and everything runs and functions exactly as it should. This is a rare find for buyers who want a top-quality used car without the new-car price tag \u2014 don't miss your chance to own something truly special!",
      "price": 47000.0,
