      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in good condition \u2014 it is a solid, well-maintained car that offers reliable everyday performance and presents well overall. The exterior shows only minor cosmetic wear consistent with normal use, such as light surface scratches and small scuffs here and there, but no significant dents or structural damage. The paint retains good color and shine across most panels. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing modest wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and door panels, but no tears or major staining. All primary controls, electronics, and comfort features operate as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and starts reliably; routine maintenance has been kept up, and there are no known mechanical issues. The tires have reasonable tread remaining, and the brakes feel responsive. This is a car you can drive with confidence \u2014 not a showpiece, but a dependable, honest vehicle that has been cared for. Buyers are welcome to arrange an independent inspection, and we encourage it.",
